WEBVTT

00:01.235 --> 00:03.461
Dakota: I wouldn't be
standing here

00:03.463 --> 00:05.362
if Alicia didn't stick
her neck out for me.

00:05.364 --> 00:07.381
Teddy: Now, you and the folks
you came here with

00:07.383 --> 00:11.543
destroyed everything
we have been working toward.

00:11.545 --> 00:13.295
Years of work.

00:13.297 --> 00:14.871
You destroyed it!

00:14.873 --> 00:16.224
♪♪

00:16.226 --> 00:18.159
What do you want?

00:18.161 --> 00:20.286
To save you, Alicia.

00:20.288 --> 00:21.996
I don't need saving.

00:21.998 --> 00:25.024
I know you don't believe in
this, [Chuckles] but you will.

00:27.218 --> 00:30.963
♪♪

